<HEADLINE> Stock Prices Fall in London / British Stocks  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LONDON (AP) -- Share prices fell Monday on the London Stock  
Exchange. 
</P>
<P>
	The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-share index was down 7.2  
points, or 0.1 percent, at 6,348.8. 
</P>
<P>
	Provisional volume was 859 million shares, compared with 1.0  
billion shares Friday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
